data.description: Welcome to this stately 5-bed, 4-bath East facing home in the sought-after subdivision of Tiberon on The Etowah.  Enjoy the welcoming rocking chair porch.  This spacious home boasts an open floor plan, which includes a dining room big enough to fit all your friends and family. Need more room? How about a bright and oversized chef's Kitchen with an expansive island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry and a butler's pantry.  Some of the features of this home include high-quality engineered hardwood floors, as well as an open living room with a cozy gas fireplace for chilly nights. The upper-level primary suite is complete with a separate area perfect for a home office or retreat, a fireplace, en suite bath, lots of natural light and a large walk in closet, providing ample space for all your wardrobe needs.  There are 4 other bedrooms, one on the main level with a full bath. Enjoy the outdoors with gazebo and expansive patio overlooking the professionally landscaped yard, including landscape lighting, privacy fence and a new brick retaining wall. This beautiful home is located on a quiet cul-de-sac and minutes away from schools, shopping, parks, and dining.  Don't miss out on this opportunity!
